Program: Outlook
Title: Mumbai Bombings
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbscf
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The 3rd year medical student who helped treat victims of the Mumbai train bombings. Also, Sakchai Makao from Thailand who lives on the Shetland Islands tells how he has beaten deportation with help from locals. The 18 year old Delhi tour guide who takes visitors off the beaten track. The migrant workers in China forced to live apart from their children. Finally eating competitions in the USA. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less